The '''Chanterelle''' is found via [[foraging]] in the [[Secret Woods]] in the [[Fall]] or grown in [[The Cave|The Farm Cave]] if the Mushroom option is chosen.  It may also be found in the [[Ginger Island#Dig Site|Ginger Island Mushroom Cave]].

==Gifting==
{{GiftsByItem
|neutral=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Kent,Marnie,Gus,Sandy
|dislike=Sebastian,Pierre,Caroline,Haley,Leo,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Sam,Shane,Elliott,Dwarf,Wizard,Willy,Krobus
|like=Linus,Leah,Harvey
}}

==Bundles==
Chanterelle is not used in any [[bundles]].

==Recipes==
Despite the numbers listed on the tooltip, the [[Life Elixir]] will fully restore [[Health]] to maximum regardless of how low it is.
{{Recipes|header|hide=buff,duration}}
{{:Life Elixir|RecipeRow/NoBuffs}}
{{Recipes|footer}}

==Tailoring==
Chanterelle is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create an {{name|Shirt015|link=Tailoring{{!}}Orange Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a brown dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the orange dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
Chanterelle is not used in any [[quests]].

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}
{{History|1.5|Can be found in the Ginger Island mushroom cave.}}

